{"tid":2318403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州富力想改名為廣州藍獅 因藍獅在粤語方言有貶義的意味被拒絕","createTime":"2020-12-09T09:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T17:25:16.000Z","uid":22556,"like":464,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f469cfc5d386a872c240b16fa4b9a86dc3027a","tid":2318403,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:59:35.000Z","msg":"由於廣州富力會徽有兩隻藍色獅子，因此上周開始傳出易名為廣州藍獅。然而廣州《信息時報》指，提議受到不少反對聲音，因為中國足壇曾經出現廈門藍獅隊，藍獅兩字「在粤語方言中亦有着貶義的意味」，最終可能易名為廣州城或廣州五羊。廣州富力在1986年以瀋陽足球隊的名義創立，前身亦包括華晨汽車、瀋陽金德等前中甲球會，於2011年落戶廣州並獲富力集團入主。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20201209/s00006/1607506171600/%e4%b8%ad%e8%b6%85-%e9%9a%8a%e5%90%8d%e5%8e%bb%e5%95%86%e6%a5%ad%e5%8c%96-%e5%bb%a3%e5%b7%9e%e5%af%8c%e5%8a%9b%e5%82%b3%e6%ac%b2%e6%94%b9%e7%a8%b1%e5%bb%a3%e5%b7%9e%e8%97%8d%e7%8d%85-%e5%9b%a0%e7%b2%b5%e8%aa%9e%e8%ab%a7%e9%9f%b3%e5%85%b7%e8%b2%b6%e7%be%a9%e8%a2%ab%e5%90%a6%e6%b1%ba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20201209%2Fs00006%2F1607506171600%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e8%25b6%2585-%25e9%259a%258a%25e5%2590%258d%25e5%258e%25bb%25e5%2595%2586%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e5%258c%2596-%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%25b7%259e%25e5%25af%258c%25e5%258a%259b%25e5%2582%25b3%25e6%25ac%25b2%25e6%2594%25b9%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%25b7%259e%25e8%2597%258d%25e7%258d%2585-%25e5%259b%25a0%25e7%25b2%25b5%25e8%25aa%259e%25e8%25ab%25a7%25e9%259f%25b3%25e5%2585%25b7%25e8%25b2%25b6%25e7%25be%25a9%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e5%2590%25a6%25e6%25b1%25ba&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=4cf20310\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20201209%2Fs00006%2F1607506171600%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e8%25b6%2585-%25e9%259a%258a%25e5%2590%258d%25e5%258e%25bb%25e5%2595%2586%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e5%258c%2596-%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%25b7%259e%25e5%25af%258c%25e5%258a%259b%25e5%2582%25b